#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:1
msgid "E3005"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:3
msgid ""
"There is no such visibility for the entity (function, type, trait, and so"
" on)."
msgstr "该实体（函数、类型、trait 等）不支持这种可见性。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:5
msgid ""
"Usually, this means that you put a `priv` visibility modifier on an "
"entity that is private by default."
msgstr "通常，这表示你在默认私有的实体上使用了 `priv` 可见性修饰符。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:8
msgid ""
"See the [Access Control](/language/packages.md#access-control) section "
"for a detailed explanation on the visibility in MoonBit."
msgstr "参见 [访问控制](/language/packages.md#access-control) 一节，了解 MoonBit 可见性的详细说明。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:13
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv let value = 3 // Error: No 'priv' visibility for value.\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:19
msgid "Remove the visibility modifier from the definition of the entity:"
msgstr "移除对象定义中的可见性修饰符："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3005.md:21
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"let value = 3 // This is already `priv` by default.\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(value, content=\"3\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
